I"È<h2 id="brake-lines">Brake Lines</h2>

<p>Brand new cunifer brake lines were fitted throughout the car with proper brake unions made on a <a href="https://automec.co.uk/products/universal-flaring-tool">very good quality universal flaring tool</a>. Pipes were routed in the same way as standard except the front brake lines go through the inner wing via a rubber grommet rather than under the chassis rail. All rubber flexible hoses were also replaced.</p>
